{"tid":551364,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"【Orage台】激運票獵人 Day174 5/2【MHW】","createTime":"2018-02-05T14:42:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-05T17:11:25.000Z","uid":122942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"219bcb19050d4845500e9ebfe2aa0aa988d8ab15","tid":551364,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T14:42:37.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/5ADqP2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2F5ADqP2.gif&h=8c5a58f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大家好，我係Orage。 我會於每晚11點至2點開台玩遊戲同與觀眾聊天。<br />\n因為我極度3分鐘熱度，所以好少會一直玩同一隻Game。<br />\n有興趣嘅巴打入黎捧下場，一齊傾下計啦  <br />\n<br />\n今晚11點左右見 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.twitch.tv/oragejan \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitch.tv%2Foragejan%20&d=efTyPGwSmWvSIciG6hPrPTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=80b4cbcb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.twitch.tv/oragejan </a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/W4CK8P.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FW4CK8P.png&h=69cccb5f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n另外我開左個FB專頁，有時會PO日常野同覺得有趣嘅事，<br />\n希望巴打們可以入黎比個讚。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/oragejan\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Foragejan&d=efTyPGwSmWvSIciG6hPrPTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=3b2fa13c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/oragejan</a></div>"},{"pid":"ddfe1ba419983fd8c5001bee7d0122f70e5a7b13","tid":551364,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T14:48:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8c382e121779c1db8ec87c109f6963f2bb81019","tid":551364,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T14:48:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4de83aa0a88beafbfaca6f1cf5d69551fcd320f4","tid":551364,"uid"